<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Peter Falkensteiner zu Falkenfels</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Rücknahme der Forderung durch Alheid Prünster, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, mit, da sie Hans Murr fälschlicherweise für einen Diener des Adressaten gehalten hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_284" id="142r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_284_r1l13"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>valkenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu valkenuels </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_284_r1l14"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>valkenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> der <expan>pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>prünſt<ex>er</ex>in</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l15"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l16"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> für vns beſant vnd <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu red geſacʒt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . dıe hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l17">vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / daʒ ſıe niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> weſt als hanns Murr ʒu ır keme . denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l18">daʒ er dennoch eẅr knecht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . vnd hab Jm auch darauf ırs acʒgelts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l19">geborgt vnd ır bettgwand darcʒu gelıhen Vnd hab auch niht anders </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l20">geweſt . denn daʒ <expan>daſſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ır bettgwand in eẅr gwalt ſulle <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l21">VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır ſıe doch auf eẅr geſchrıft <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geweıſet daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l22">ſıe dıe ſache gen eẅch hat <expan>fall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l24"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l23"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> Paſche </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_284" id="142r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Valkenstein<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Valkenvels </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Valkenstein<ex>er,</ex></expan> als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
            habt von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> der <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Prünst<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> für uns besant und <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu red gesaczt <expan>habe<ex>n.</ex></expan> Die hat uns
                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt,</expan> daz sie niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
            west, als Hanns Murr zu ir keme, denn daz er dennoch ewr knecht
              <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, und hab im auch darauf irs aczgelts geborgt und ir
            bettgwand darczu gelihen und hab auch niht anders gewest denn, daz
                <expan>dass<ex>elb</ex></expan> ir bettgwand in ewr gwalt sulle
                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir sie doch auf ewr geschrift
              <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geweiset, daz sie die sache gen ewch hat
                <expan>fall<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> pasche. </ab>
</div>
